Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you can't go through with this belt...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.43,0:00:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? {\alpha&HFF&}Still doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Still doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... {\alpha&HFF&}we really don't have a choice but to accustom you to the security measures around here, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... we really don't have a choice but to accustom you to the security measures around here, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about... this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened to your forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I had a fight with my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My kid is still young, so it looks like I'm going to have to commute here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.69,0:01:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, {\alpha&HFF&}it would be better for you to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it would be better for you to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste! {\alpha&HFF&}The rooms here are incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste! The rooms here are incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just move in yourself, with the family and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like I'm a single, easy-going guy such as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.35,0:01:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A date.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.68,0:01:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone on a date, along with Light-kun, in Misa-Misa's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surveillance cameras, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\alpha&HFF&}I guess it's unavoidable considering Amane is somehow connected to the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's unavoidable considering Amane is somehow connected to the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Matsuda, stop calling her "Misa-Misa"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.72,0:01:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You know, for me, this just isn't feeling like a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:01:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, aren't you going to eat that cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet things make you fat, so I avoid them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you use your brain, you won't get fat, even if you eat sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You're making fun of Misa again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. How about I give you the cake if you leave me and Light alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I leave you alone, I'd still be watching you on the surveillance cameras; it'll still be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert! Will you just quit with all this tasteless stuff, already?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you say, I'm still taking your cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. We'll just close the curtains and turn off the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cameras detect infrared as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, {\alpha&HFF&}despite moving into these headquarters filled with equipment, Ryuuzaki, you seem to lack the motivation to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, despite moving into these headquarters filled with equipment, {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki, you seem to lack the motivation to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, despite moving into these headquarters filled with equipment, Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}you seem to lack the motivation to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, despite moving into these headquarters filled with equipment, Ryuuzaki, you seem to lack the motivation to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motivation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I'm pretty depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I've always thought that Light-kun was Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}the idea that this theory may be wrong has come as quite a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I've always thought that Light-kun was Kira, the idea that this theory may be wrong has come as quite a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I have my suspicions...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence the reason for these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then again, Kira can manipulate people's actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Kira was manipulating you in such a way that I would suspect you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Light-kun and Misa-san were being manipulated by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it this way, it does seem to make sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By that reasoning, {\alpha&HFF&}even though Misa and I were being manipulated, we were still Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By that reasoning, even though Misa and I were being manipulated, we were still Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, {\alpha&HFF&}there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my theory, Light-kun was Kira when I imprisoned him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And from that moment, criminals stopped dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, the theory that Light-kun was Kira still worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, two weeks later, {\alpha&HFF&}criminals started dying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, two weeks later, criminals started dying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So from here, we move to the next assumption...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's powers can be passed from person to person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an interesting theory, but if that's the case, then catching Kira will be no small feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's why I'm stumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we catch those being manipulated, {\alpha&HFF&}their power will just pass to someone else, and no memory of it will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we catch those being manipulated, their power will just pass to someone else, and no memory of it will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many people we manage to catch, it'll be pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But none of this has been confirmed yet. {\alpha&HFF&}Try and rouse some motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But none of this has been confirmed yet. Try and rouse some motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motivation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it's probably better if we don't try too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we chase them too desperately, we'll just be placing our own lives at risk... {\alpha&HFF&}don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we chase them too desperately, we'll just be placing our own lives at risk... don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuck with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no motivation because your little theory about me being Kira was wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I phrased that badly. {\alpha&HFF&}I meant that making the first move might work against us, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I phrased that badly. I meant that making the first move might work against us, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to catch them if we don't even chase them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many innocent people do you think have already been entangled in this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, weren't you the one who imprisoned both Misa and myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... {\alpha&HFF&}but no matter what reasons you had, my motto is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... but {\alpha&HFF&}no matter what reasons you had, my motto is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... but no matter what reasons you had, my motto is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An eye for an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that my theory was wrong, {\alpha&HFF&}merely that "Yagami Light is Kira" and "Amane Misa is the second Kira" wasn't enough to solve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that my theory was wrong, merely that "Yagami Light is Kira" and "Amane Misa is the second Kira" wasn't enough to solve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it so wrong for a human to feel this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say it was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you're talking, {\alpha&HFF&}it sounds like you won't be satisfied unless I really am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you're talking, it sounds like you won't be satisfied unless I really am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not satisfied unless Light-kun really is Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only just realized... {\alpha&HFF&}I wanted you to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only just realized... I wanted you to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, an eye for an eye.
