Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how's that? {\alpha&HFF&}Feeling slightly more motivated now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how's that? Feeling slightly more motivated now?
Comment: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impressive that everything is going this smoothly; nobody suspects anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Yotsuba's share price and profits have gradually been rising without gaining attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going exactly according to our calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just one thing that's been on my mind... {\alpha&HFF&}the three we killed last week... why did they all die of heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just one thing that's been on my mind... the three we killed last week... {\alpha&HFF&}why did they all die of heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just one thing that's been on my mind... the three we killed last week... why did they all die of heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For one of them, I thought we decided on an accidental death?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably because we specified the place of death as along the Wangansen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, at the time of his death, he wasn't at home, but was secretly with a woman in Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, {\alpha&HFF&}if there's an impossible element in the cause of death we provide...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if there's an impossible element in the cause of death we provide...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will merely kill them with a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said last week that if we just request for a death either via an accident or illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll eliminate them in the fastest and most natural way possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, {\alpha&HFF&}the police should already have their hands full investigating the deaths of criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the police should already have their hands full investigating the deaths of criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was someone who was able to trace these civilian deaths back to us, {\alpha&HFF&}they would have to be some sort of god.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was someone who was able to trace these civilian deaths back to us, they would have to be some sort of god.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, it's all been taken care of already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! {\alpha&HFF&}Ah, Mogi-san! Thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Ah, {\alpha&HFF&}Mogi-san! Thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Ah, Mogi-san! {\alpha&HFF&}Thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Ah, Mogi-san! Thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing! {\alpha&HFF&}Thanks to Light-kun's work, there's a real possibility that Kira is connected to the Yotsuba Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing! Thanks to Light-kun's work, there's a real possibility that Kira is connected to the Yotsuba Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably it, Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, {\alpha&HFF&}I heard from the Deputy Chief that Kira has been sending bribes to politicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:10:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, I heard from the Deputy Chief that Kira has been sending bribes to politicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what Kira is promising... {\alpha&HFF&}in return for the police simply ceasing their pursuit of Kira, they would leave the politicians untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what Kira is promising... in return for the police simply ceasing their pursuit of Kira, they would leave the politicians untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police have sold out to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi has already made his decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, {\alpha&HFF&}Matsuda, if you still want to pursue Kira, you'll need to follow Mogi and myself, and hand in your resignations to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, Matsuda, {\alpha&HFF&}if you still want to pursue Kira, you'll need to follow Mogi and myself, and hand in your resignations to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, Matsuda, if you still want to pursue Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}you'll need to follow Mogi and myself, and hand in your resignations to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, Matsuda, if you still want to pursue Kira, you'll need to follow Mogi and myself, and hand in your resignations to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we decide to resign from the police, {\alpha&HFF&}we'll no longer be allowed to investigate Kira seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we decide to resign from the police, we'll no longer be allowed to investigate Kira seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very simple. {\alpha&HFF&}They said that if I continue to investigate with L, I'll be fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very simple. They said that if I continue to investigate with L, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll be fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very simple. They said that if I continue to investigate with L, I'll be fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}So, Chief, what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So, Chief, what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a few hours, I'll no longer be the Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have your own lives, {\alpha&HFF&}so think carefully before you decide what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have your own lives, so think carefully before you decide what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, {\alpha&HFF&}especially those with wives and children...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:11:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, especially those with wives and children...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that all of you should return to the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I originally began alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful that you've all managed to stick with it for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll be able to do this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I promise to visit you all with Kira's head as a present to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}as long as I'm here, you won't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, as long as I'm here, you won't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made this promise as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct. {\alpha&HFF&}Until Kira is caught, I'll need Yagami-kun to stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct. Until Kira is caught, I'll need Yagami-kun to stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the rest of you should return to the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you once say that you needed the cooperation of the police with this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was because then, the police, as an organization, was prepared to disobey Kira and maintain its stance on this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But help from a few civilians who have quit the police can't really be said to be with "the cooperation of the police".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:12:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police have decided not to catch Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}You've done enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police have decided not to catch Kira. You've done enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true that if we leave the police, we may not be of much help to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what about our feelings?! {\alpha&HFF&}We've put our lives on the line for this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what about our feelings?! We've put our lives on the line for this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have the right to decide by ourselves: do we want to continue investigating, or return to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so... {\alpha&HFF&}in that case, please make your own decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so... in that case, please make your own decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-{\alpha&HFF&}But Chief, by quitting the police we'll be without a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Chief, {\alpha&HFF&}by quitting the police we'll be without a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Chief, by quitting the police we'll be without a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we manage to catch Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}what are we supposed to do after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we manage to catch Kira, what are we supposed to do after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that? {\alpha&HFF&}I hadn't really thought of that, but I'm guessing that once we've caught Kira, we'd have to... find new jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that? I hadn't really thought of that, {\alpha&HFF&}but I'm guessing that once we've caught Kira, we'd have to... find new jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that? I hadn't really thought of that, but I'm guessing that once we've caught Kira, we'd have to... {\alpha&HFF&}find new jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that? I hadn't really thought of that, but I'm guessing that once we've caught Kira, we'd have to... find new jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided! {\alpha&HFF&}I'm going to quit the police and continue chasing Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided! I'm going to quit the police and continue chasing Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a job as Misa-Misa's manager, besides, if I return to the police, I'd feel like a loser--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch what you say, Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible to return to the police, and help out in my spare time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}If you're planning to return to the police, please don't come here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. If you're planning to return to the police, please don't come here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I won't reveal a single thing from this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely won't give you any information from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to pursue Kira as a lone policeman, then that's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it'd be right for you to quit as a police officer, and then go chasing Kira to the point of causing your family concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly as Ryuuzaki says. {\alpha&HFF&}If you decide to stop now, no one will blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly as Ryuuzaki says. If you decide to stop now, no one will blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. {\alpha&HFF&}We won't think of you as a traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We won't think of you as a traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Chief, you also have a family...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our circumstances are completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so unfair. {\alpha&HFF&}I wanted to stay as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so unfair. I wanted to stay as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:14:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I approached this knowing that my life was going to be at risk...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I quit now, how can I face Ukita?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! {\alpha&HFF&}Why has it become wrong for a police officer to chase Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why has it become wrong for a police officer to chase Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki... {\alpha&HFF&}didn't you make me promise that if anything happens to any member of the investigation, including being fired by the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki... didn't you make me promise that if anything happens to any member of the investigation, {\alpha&HFF&}including being fired by the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki... didn't you make me promise that if anything happens to any member of the investigation, including being fired by the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would provide them and their family with sufficient financial aid for a lifetime?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you reluctant to tell them this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business, Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? {\alpha&HFF&}You've even acted to protect our livelihood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You've even acted to protect our livelihood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great, Aizawa-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}were you testing me to see whether I'd leave the police and continue here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, were you testing me to see whether I'd leave the police and continue here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}It isn't like that, Aizawa! Ryuuzaki just hates to say things like that himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It isn't like that, Aizawa! {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki just hates to say things like that himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It isn't like that, Aizawa! Ryuuzaki just hates to say things like that himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:14:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was testing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see what choice he'd make.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I get it! {\alpha&HFF&}I'm leaving this investigation and returning to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I get it! I'm leaving this investigation and returning to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was unable to make an instant decision like you, {\alpha&HFF&}and was leaning towards returning to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was unable to make an instant decision like you, and was leaning towards returning to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to be stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! {\alpha&HFF&}I quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just realized... {\alpha&HFF&}I hate Ryuuzaki, his methods, all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just realized... I hate Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}his methods, all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just realized... I hate Ryuuzaki, his methods, all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Aizawa-san, {\alpha&HFF&}I like people that are like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Aizawa-san, I like people that are like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the other thing I hate! {\alpha&HFF&}The fact that you can say that with such a straight face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the other thing I hate! The fact that you can say that with such a straight face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A branch manager from one of Yotsuba's biggest rival banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,September 7th - slipped on the stairs at home and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,September 7th, that makes it a Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking a look at this again, {\alpha&HFF&}it just occurred to me that all the deaths which benefit Yotsuba happen towards the end of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking a look at this again, it just occurred to me that all the deaths which benefit Yotsuba happen towards the end of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? {\alpha&HFF&}Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first the times of death were random; {\alpha&HFF&}however, they've gradually begun to cluster around the time from Friday evening until Saturday afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first the times of death were random; however, they've gradually begun to cluster around the time from Friday evening until Saturday afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an excellent observation, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you that I'm not "Chief" anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}To me, you'll always be the Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. To me, you'll always be the Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an excellent lead, father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not planning to lose to you and Ryuuzaki just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be a dead weight around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead weight...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kira a part of Yotsuba? {\alpha&HFF&}Is Kira merely using Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kira a part of Yotsuba? Is Kira merely using Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no idea which it is, {\alpha&HFF&}but we can assume that Kira is behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no idea which it is, but we can assume that Kira is behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time that we investigate Yotsuba thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finished compiling a list of all Yotsuba's employees, both here and overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over 300,000 people! {\alpha&HFF&}How did he manage this so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over 300,000 people! How did he manage this so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Mogi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was always something amazing about Mogi-san, right from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki, is there anything else I can do? Other than being a manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}is there anything else I can do? Other than being a manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki, is there anything else I can do? {\alpha&HFF&}Other than being a manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki, is there anything else I can do? Other than being a manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to make yourself useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, can you bring me another cup of coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't forget our guests as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did they get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're our new members.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aiber, {\alpha&HFF&}a con artist. Nice to meet ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aiber, a con artist. {\alpha&HFF&}Nice to meet ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aiber, a con artist. Nice to meet ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Weddy, {\alpha&HFF&}a thief by trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Weddy, a thief by trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-{\alpha&HFF&}A con artist and a thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A con artist and a thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiber acquires and learns what is necessary for every social discourse, and is guaranteed to form an intimate connection with his target.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be using him as our spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weddy is a thief that can crack any safe, key or security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof, she was able to infiltrate this place without anyone noticing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}We'll be investigating with criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We'll be investigating with criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're criminals, {\alpha&HFF&}but not the type that appear in public. Kira will not be able to judge them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're criminals, but not the type that appear in public. Kira will not be able to judge them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to think of them as professionals from the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. {\alpha&HFF&}In order to investigate Yotsuba properly, we'll need such people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. In order to investigate Yotsuba properly, we'll need such people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all work together on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi... {\alpha&HFF&}Eriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi... Eriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to come home, just say so. {\alpha&HFF&}I haven't bought you any dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to come home, just say so. I haven't bought you any dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you half of my croquettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... {\alpha&HFF&}I haven't had a lot of rest, so they've given me some leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I haven't had a lot of rest, so they've given me some leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Leave"? You have time off?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I should get some time off every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we can come to this park... {\alpha&HFF&}even the zoo... or theme parks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we can come to this park... even the zoo... {\alpha&HFF&}or theme parks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we can come to this park... even the zoo... or theme parks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama... {\alpha&HFF&}papa is crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama... papa is crying.
